---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="404" description="Not found">
    <main class="container">
        <hgroup>
            <h2>Not found</h2>
        </hgroup>
        <img src="http://http.cat/404" alt="funny cat image with 404 code on it" width="50%" loading="lazy"> <br />
        <p>Hey wanderer, this page is not here. Don't be sad tho, that could also mean that it is just not public yet!</p>
        <p>If you think that this is an issue <a href="/#contact">contact me</a>.</p>

        <p>Requested URL: <code>{Astro.url.searchParams.has("source")?Astro.url.searchParams.get("source"):Astro.url.pathname}</code></p>
    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
    main {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
    }
</style>